SCHEMA: time/intent_log.schema
schema_id: dominium.schema.time.intent_log
schema_version: 1.0.0
stability: core

PURPOSE:
- Define deterministic chunked intent-log artifacts.

REQUIRED SHAPE:
record intent_log
  required:
    - schema_version: semver
    - log_id: id
    - save_id: id
    - tick_range: map
    - envelopes_or_intents: [id]
    - log_hash: sha256
    - extensions: map
